{"tid":1296552,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Lisa穿超低胸被拍…「解放事業線」辣翻！","createTime":"2019-07-08T11:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T05:45:30.000Z","uid":74065,"like":8,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"93682acabae714b49730d89183af801857c2e247","tid":1296552,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4220/4220904.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4220%2F4220904.jpg&h=bb3fcfdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lisa為BLACKPINK成員。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／Lisa）<br />\n<br />\nLisa擁有一雙水汪汪的大眼睛，甜美又精緻的長相，讓她被封為「人間芭比」，她7日在Instagram曬出自己的照片，只見她上衣外面搭著白色罩衫，裡面則穿著黑色平口上衣，胸前低胸的設計，更是讓她的事業線呼之欲出，若穩若現，模樣非常性感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4220/4220905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4220%2F4220905.jpg&h=7795cf43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lisa罕見地小露事業線。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／Lisa）<br />\n<br />\n而Lisa除了擁有精緻臉蛋，她還有一雙眾所皆知的纖細美腿，她曬出美照後，罕見小露性感的她，隨即釣出大票粉絲，更紛紛留言大讚：「天啊好辣」、「Lisa好美」、「根本芭比娃娃啊」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4220/4220912.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4220%2F4220912.jpg&h=6a2bd219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4220/4220913.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4220%2F4220913.jpg&h=a681d287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lisa身材超好，一雙美腿又細又長。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／Lisa）"},{"pid":"57aeae6c69f640a4a6a960082e611685e16ae3e3","tid":1296552,"uid":193951,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:53:53.000Z","msg":"台狗啲標題真係好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6776a6fd2a49ffedd8474ec47dff08ba134fa29e","tid":1296552,"uid":48577,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac